Note 1: "??" ranges from 01 to 63 only.
Note 2: If you are starting a new game, you must train the monster once
before applying the code.
Note 3: Max Stats Info: Enable all the codes. Turn the shark off,
make your monster work and the stats will level out to its max stats.
Note 4: May have to be used with the Item Modifier/Item Info Modifier
code as well for that slot. If this doesn't work for your inventory, it will
work for the shops inventory. Just buy what you want from it.
Note 5: Make sure the monster you want
to keep normal is frozen before activating code! Activate the code with
whatever monster you want to make! Then go to the market an buy a
Dino and freeze it. Then make a second Dino in the
market...freeze it, turn shark OFF then combine the two dinos to make a
full breed of whatever creature you programmed the shark for.
Note 6: This will show that your monster is 999 years old but really
isn't....once code is applied give your monster a rest and he'll wake up all
grown up.
Note 7: This is the sub-type monster code which gives you the
mix breeds and rare monster.
